<div class="thank-you-page">
  <div class="content">
    <div class="success-icon">
      <svg
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        stroke-width="2.5"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
      >
        <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <h2>THANK YOU</h2>
    <p>
      ポートフォリオを最後までご覧いただき、<br />誠にありがとうございました。
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .thank-you-page {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: transparent;
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .success-icon {
    width: 64px;
    height: 64px;
    background: #111;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 12px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    color: #111;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #444;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-family: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
  }
</style>
